query: How many transactions were made by customers who have a loan?
What is the total balance of accounts belonging to customers who also have a deposit?
What is the number of customers who have both a loan and a deposit?
sql_command:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c.customer_id)
FROM banking_new."Customers" c
JOIN banking_new."Deposits" d ON c.customer_id = d.customer_id
JOIN banking_new."Loans" l ON c.customer_id = l.customer_id;

query: What is the total loan balance for customers who own at least one card?
sql_command:
SELECT SUM("Loans".balance) AS total_loan_balance
FROM banking_new."Customers"
JOIN banking_new."Cards" ON "Customers".customer_id = "Cards".customer_id
JOIN banking_new."Loans" ON "Customers".customer_id = "Loans".customer_id
WHERE "Cards".is_blocked = false;

query: What is the total deposit balance for customers who made at least one transaction?
sql_command:
SELECT SUM(D.balance) AS total_deposit_balance
FROM banking_new."Deposits" D
JOIN banking_new."Customers" C ON D.customer_id = C.customer_id
JOIN banking_new."Accounts" A ON C.customer_id = A.customer_id
JOIN banking_new."Transactions" T ON A.account_id = T.account_id;

query: How many transactions were made by customers who belong to branch 1?
sql_command:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS transaction_count
FROM banking_new."Transactions"
JOIN banking_new."Accounts" ON banking_new."Transactions".account_id = banking_new."Accounts".account_id
JOIN banking_new."Customers" ON banking_new."Accounts".customer_id = banking_new."Customers".customer_id
WHERE banking_new."Customers".branch_id = 1;

query: What is the total number of accounts for customers who belong to each branch?
What is the number of customers with more than one account?
sql_command:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT customer_id) AS num_customers_with_multiple_accounts
FROM banking_new."Accounts"
GROUP BY customer_id
HAVING COUNT(account_id) > 1;

query: What is the number of customers with more than one loan?

query: What is the number of blocked cards belonging to customers with loans?

query: What is the number of expired cards belonging to customers with deposits?

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c.card_id) AS expired_cards_count
FROM banking_new."Cards" c
JOIN banking_new."Customers" cu ON c.customer_id = cu.customer_id
JOIN banking_new."Deposits" d ON cu.customer_id = d.customer_id
WHERE c.expiration_date < CURRENT_DATE

query: What is the number of accounts created before 2020 for customers with loans?

query: What is the number of deposits created after 2021 for customers with cards?

WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1

query: Count the number of accounts per branch with ID 125.
Count the number of transactions with amount greater than average per branch.

SELECT 
    b.branch_code, 
    COUNT(t.transaction_id) AS transaction_count
FROM 
    banking_new."Branches" b
JOIN 
    banking_new."Customers" c ON b.branch_id = c.branch_id
JOIN 
    banking_new."Accounts" a ON c.customer_id = a.customer_id
JOIN 
    banking_new."Transactions" t ON a.account_id = t.account_id
GROUP BY 
    b.branch_code
HAVING 
    COUNT(t.transaction_id) > (
        SELECT 
            AVG(transaction_count)
        FROM (
            SELECT 
                COUNT(t.transaction_id) AS transaction_count
            FROM 
                banking_new."Branches" b
            JOIN 
                banking_new."Customers" c ON b.branch_id = c.branch_id
            JOIN 
                banking_new."Accounts" a ON c.customer_id = a.customer_id
            JOIN 
                banking_new."Transactions" t ON a.account_id = t.account_id

                b.branch_id

    );
